msgid "WooCommerce Contacts"
msgstr "Contactos de WooCommerce"

#: admin/class-doppler-for-woocommerce-admin.php:260
msgid ""
"Ouch! <strong>Doppler for WooCommerce</strong> requires the <a "
"href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/doppler-form/\">Doppler Forms</a> "
"plugin to be installed and active."
msgstr ""
"¡Ouch! <strong>Doppler para WooCommerce</strong> requiere que tengas el "
"plugin Formularios Doppler instalado y activo."

#: admin/class-doppler-for-woocommerce-admin.php:264
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Ouch! <strong>Doppler for WooCommerce</strong> requires at least "
"<strong>Doppler Forms %1$s</strong> to be active. Please <a "
"href=\"%2$splugins.php\">upgrade</a> Doppler Forms."
msgstr ""
"¡Ouch! <strong>Doppler para WooCommerce</strong> requiere al menos "
"<strong>Doppler Forms v%1$s</strong> para  poder activarse. Por favor <a "
"href=\"%2$splugins.php\">actualiza</a> Doppler Forms."

